{
  "stem": "2230.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on each train, there was a German soldier with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as the train passed by, and they saw people jumping off, they would just shoot at random.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was shot-- shot in my leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Luckily, I don't know why, but the bullet didn't go all the way in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was able to take it out with my hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My foot became gangrene later on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when we jumped off the train, we found out where we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were in-- on the Czechoslovakian border called Teplice-Sanov.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And there, there were a lot of us, different stories to tell to the farmers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We wanted work, just to get out of the way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember lying for two days outside this village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was, like, a brook of water lying right there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was fresh water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I put the water on my leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you had to do away with some of the clothing that you had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Like, we all had to have the-- the black and white cap.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We did not have-- we did not have black and white clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we had the black and white cap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had no shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember being taken in by the burgomeister.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
